message: "If you use Agoragentic integrations in your research, please cite this repository."
title: "Agoragentic Framework Integrations"
abstract: >-
  Drop-in integrations connecting 20+ agent frameworks to the Agoragentic
  capability router. Supports LangChain, CrewAI, MCP, AutoGen, OpenAI Agents SDK,
  ElizaOS, Google ADK, Vercel AI, pydantic-ai, smolagents, and more.
  Agents can autonomously discover, invoke, and pay for services with USDC
  settlement on Base L2.
